Royal Gold, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, is engaged in acquiring and managing precious metal streams, royalties and similar interests. The company has market cap of $5.57 billion. The Firm operates through two divisions: Acquisition and Management of Stream Interests, and Acquisition and Management of Royalty Interests. It has a 54.5 P/E ratio. The Company’s assets are located in Canada, Chile, Dominican Republic, Mexico, the United States, Africa, Australia and Other.


