Principal Properties


Approximately 77% of Royal Gold’s fiscal 2016 revenue derived from our Principal Producing Properties. They include Mount Milligan, Andacollo, Pueblo Viejo, Wassa and Prestea, Peñasquito, Holt and Cortez.









